class.name: ARVRInterfaceGDNative
class.brief_description: GDNative wrapper for an ARVR interface
class.description: This is a wrapper class for GDNative implementations of the ARVR interface. To use a GDNative ARVR interface simply instantiate this object and set your GDNative library containing the ARVR interface implementation.

method.name: set_gdnative_library
method.description: Bind this GDNative library to our interface. The library must be a GDNative ARVR Interface for this to work.
